quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  38,27,"And We have not created the heaven and the earth and all that is between them without purpose; this is what the disbelievers assume; therefore ruin is for the disbelievers, by the fire."
  38,28,"Shall We make those who believe and do good deeds equal to those who spread turmoil in the earth? Or shall We equate the pious with the disobedient?"
  38,29,"This is a Book which We have sent down upon you, a blessed Book, for them to ponder upon its verses, and for men of intellect to accept advice."
  38,30,"And We bestowed Sulaiman to Dawud; what an excellent bondman! He is indeed most inclined."
  38,31,"When fast footed steeds were presented to him at evening."
  38,32,"Therefore Sulaiman said, “I cherish the love of these horses*, out of remembrance of my Lord”; he then ordered them to be raced until they vanished in a curtain out of sight. (To be used in holy war.)"
  38,33,"He then ordered, “Bring them back to me”; and he began caressing their shins and necks."
  38,34,"And We indeed tested Sulaiman, and placed a dead body on his throne – he therefore inclined towards His Lord."
  38,35,"He said, “My Lord! Forgive me and bestow upon me a kingdom, which shall not befit anyone after me; indeed only You are the Great Bestower.”"
  38,36,"We therefore gave the wind under his control, moving steadily by his command wherever he wished."
  38,37,"And made the demons subservient to him, all builders and divers."
  38,38,"And other demons bound in chains."
  38,39,"“This is Our bestowal – you may therefore bestow favours or withhold them – you will not be questioned.”"
  38,40,"And indeed for him in Our presence are, surely, proximity and an excellent abode."
  38,41,"And remember Our bondman Ayyub (Job); when he cried out* to his Lord, “The devil has struck me with hardship and pain.” (After seven years of patience.)"
  38,42,"We said to him, “Strike the earth with your foot; this cool spring is for bathing and drinking.” (A spring of gushed forth when he struck the earth – this was a miracle.)"
